3232
03:09:03.665 --> 03:09:06.175
These facilities are more than just places to ride.

3233
03:09:06.805 --> 03:09:08.175
They're safe, inclusive,

3234
03:09:08.475 --> 03:09:10.775
and accessible spaces that support youth development,

3235
03:09:11.075 --> 03:09:13.335
active recreation, and community connection.

3236
03:09:13.925 --> 03:09:16.135
They've become focal points for volunteering

3237
03:09:16.155 --> 03:09:18.615
and community spirit drawing in families

3238
03:09:18.635 --> 03:09:20.655
and supporters from across the region.

3239
03:09:21.605 --> 03:09:23.375
Importantly, pump tracks

3240
03:09:23.375 --> 03:09:25.895
and BMX are gateways to community, recreation

3241
03:09:25.915 --> 03:09:28.295
and structured sport for many young people.

3242
03:09:28.545 --> 03:09:31.175
These facilities are the first step into healthy activity,

3243
03:09:31.725 --> 03:09:34.575
community events, and a lifelong love of movement.

3244
03:09:35.415 --> 03:09:38.335
B MX is not only an Olympic sport in its own right where

3245
03:09:38.915 --> 03:09:40.735
ROA has achieved remarkable success,

3246
03:09:41.275 --> 03:09:44.055
but is also a proven feeder for other cycling disciplines,

3247
03:09:44.455 --> 03:09:46.895
mountain biking, track cycling, and road cycling.

3248
03:09:47.875 --> 03:09:50.815
New Zealand is renowned worldwide for its venous spirit,

3249
03:09:51.285 --> 03:09:53.700
outdoor lifestyle and commitment to wellbeing.

3250
03:09:54.225 --> 03:09:57.045
Our success across cycling disciplines on the world stage is

3251
03:09:57.085 --> 03:09:58.245
a reflection of these values.

3252
03:09:59.145 --> 03:10:01.445
By investing in grassroots facilities like ours,

3253
03:10:01.785 --> 03:10:03.805
we are not only nurturing future champions,

3254
03:10:04.265 --> 03:10:06.245
but also reinforcing New Zealand's reputation.

3255
03:10:06.245 --> 03:10:08.445
As a country where adventure, fun,

3256
03:10:08.545 --> 03:10:10.405
and health are part of our national identity,

3257
